node.text: So tomorrow kicks off Icast 2021 for all us professional anglers in this industry.  So the timing couldn’t be more perfect for me to share this awesome piece @columbiapfg did called #WhyIFish .  I never really asked myself this question in all these years but it all came out here.  Check it out and tell me why you fish.  #MDJfishing #WhyIFish #ColumbiaPFG

node.text: Shout out to all my bank fisherman out there.  This always brings me back to the beginning.  Before boats, electeonics, and traveling the nation there was the good ole Bank.  Whether its wading in the creek or beating the bank at the local lake, I just love getting back to the basics.  Just uploaded the latest Vid on fall time Bank fishing.  check em out!  link in Bio #MDJfishing #BankFishing #FallTime #BackToTheBasics

node.text: I cant thank @billlewisfishing enough for giving me the opportunity to create my own signature series line of crank baits. when I tell you this MR6 has bailed me out, I mean it and several times at that.  Last period on day two I was outside the cut when I picked up ole faithful (Louisiana shad) and caught back to back scoreable bass to bring back inside the cut with 30min left.  I'm telling you this crank is super legit. #MDJfishing #MR6 #SavedTheDay #BillLewisFishing #MajorLeagueFishing

node.text: So tomorrow kicks off Icast 2021 for all us professional anglers in this industry.  So the timing couldn’t be more perfect for me to share this awesome piece @columbiapfg did called #WhyIFish .  I never really asked myself this question in all these years but it all came out here.  Check it out and tell me why you fish.  #MDJfishing #WhyIFish #ColumbiaPFG

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Mark Daniels Jr. in Richmond, California. May be an image of 1 person, child, standing and text that says 'S RDING SCHOOL'.

node.text: #FBF This was my first ever bait casting reel (Daiwa black widow) my parents brought for me.  You can’t tell in the pic but I was Hella juiced and thought I was KVD😂😂!! This was the first puzzle piece of a lifetime obsession!! P.s you a real one if you went to Harding Elementary school 😂☝🏾!! #MDJfishing #TheStart #ItwasAllaDream #1992

node.text: Been sitting on this one for a while now but it’s finally here.  My new signature series flipping stick by @favoriterodsusa is one bad dude.  I couldn’t be more excited.  I’ll put all the details in my story with a swipe up so you can check out the 🔥🔥 #MDJfishing #NewStick #FlippingStick #SheBad #GetYours

node.text: We fought hard but when the dust settled we came up short.  Still a great week catching big brownies up here at the St. Lawrance.  What a special place!! We’ll bounce back at Champlain 💯🤞🏾 #MDJfishing 📷: @garrickdixondesigns

node.text: And it was at this moment I knew I had messed up 😂😂!! In all seriousness, I was happy to catch him although I was targeting smallmouth. Time to right the ship come Monday and make a big move☝🏾!! #MDJfishing #Bycatch #goodaccident #LetsMakeThatCut

node.text: Good ole Lake Chickamauga 😅😅!! Man we have a love hate relationship lol She kicked my butt last week but I can say I learned a lot after the fact watching live.  Sometimes your so close yet so far.  Shout out my boy J Dub and his wife for the great hospitality all week.  Back for my sons graduation then off to NY, home of the Dodo smallmouth✌🏾!! #MDJfishing #Lessons #Offshorefishing #GottaDoBetter
